{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The House of Toys is a game developed by Old School Bros, a duo of video game and horror genre enthusiasts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game's mission is to free the soul of the cursed toy, day after day, game after game. But be careful\u2014each game can be different. You will earn rewards that make your work more satisfying, allow you to improve your room, and help you discover secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The House of Toys is divided into several phases in each game.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Phase 1:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Investigate \u2013 Explore the mansion, searching for clues to help you identify the toy.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Phase 2:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Puzzles and Action \u2013 While avoiding the cursed toy, you\u2019ll need to solve puzzles that grant you the power to free its soul.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Phase 3:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stealth \u2013 You\u2019ll need to be cautious and stealthy to use your new power and release the toy\u2019s soul.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Do you dare to discover the true origin of the curse?</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321000/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737373078","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321000/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737373078","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321000/41db53513e5ba07a08fc6c582bcff62ae0158db6/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737373078","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321000/41db53513e5ba07a08fc6c582bcff62ae0158db6/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737373078","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The House of Toys is a game developed by Old School Bros, a duo of video game and horror genre enthusiasts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game's mission is to free the soul of the cursed toy, day after day, game after game. But be careful\u2014each game can be different. You will earn rewards that make your work more satisfying, allow you to improve your room, and help you discover secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The House of Toys is divided into several phases in each game.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Phase 1:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Investigate \u2013 Explore the mansion, searching for clues to help you identify the toy.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Phase 2:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Puzzles and Action \u2013 While avoiding the cursed toy, you\u2019ll need to solve puzzles that grant you the power to free its soul.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Phase 3:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stealth \u2013 You\u2019ll need to be cautious and stealthy to use your new power and release the toy\u2019s soul.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Do you dare to discover the true origin of the curse?</p>","developers":["Old School Bros"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321000/header.jpg?t=1737373078","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257090555,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257090555/movie480.mp4?t=1